data.title: Private All Boys Prep School in Mendota Heights, Minnesota
data.meta_description: Saint Thomas Academy is an all boys private prep school serving Mendota Heights, St. Paul, & Eagan. Strong academics & athletics programs. Learn more!
data.text:
Join us as we host this annual tradition for grandparents' and their grandsons.

Thursday, September 26

8:00 a.m. - 11:45 a.m.

The event will include a complimentary photo opportunity and lunch with your grandson, tours of school, Crack Drill Squad performances, Mass, and an Upper School Pass and Review.
